item.title: #TIL 2017-02-23 : Random quote 23 Feb 2017
item.description: Random quote 23 Feb 2017 A computer lets you make more mistakes faster than any other invention in human history, with the possible exceptions of handguns and tequila. - Mitch Ratcliffe Haha, it’s totally true ! And it makes me remember this meme when I was little bit drunk !
